_sText:
==========cs_panda_house==========

   =======   Alpha 1.0  =======

     =====  by P.Panda  =====     

A medium large circle house map 
including a small garden,many 
glasses, different vents and a
small river in the middle.
It is very funny to play this map
even if the textures aren't 
that good until now and there 
aren't many models included yet.
But I just want to get some feed-
back, how you like the map and
what you would improve. So please
tell me something about your ex-
periences and other. 
I also need two more persons:
1 for making a good .nav file
and
1 for making an overview, because
I don't know how to do it xD
And those need to be pleased with
a note in the credits including 
their names and a short note.
So, if you are interested and if
you are able to talk to a german
guy speaking english like a dummy,
then send me a PM and tell me
something about you.

NOTE: The map includes many 
texture bugs at the moment, but I 
had no time to correct them until 
now, so please just rate the
gameplay and not the look first.


Thanks,
P.Panda
